      <view class="version-date">2026-07-14</view>
      <view class="version-copy">优化汇率换算输入、删除、小数位显示和计算器展开交互。</view>
    </view>
    <view class="version-item">
      <view class="version-head">
        <text class="version-name">v1.0.0</text>
        <text class="version-status">基础版本</text>
      </view>
      <view class="version-date">2026-07-12</view>
      <view class="version-copy">首个版本，手搓的要崩溃了，颈椎病都犯了。</view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="about-footer">Reliable · Efficient · Precise</view>
</view>

<view class="bottom-nav about-nav">
  <view class="nav-item" bindtap="goHome">
